text: Daniel Masters (born 7 December 1986) is an English cricketer who played in three List A matches for Leicestershire in 2009 and 2010.Daniel Masters at CricketArchiveDaniel Masters at ESPNCricinfo He was born in Chatham, Kent and is the son of Kevin Masters, who played first-class cricket for Kent and the brother of David Masters who played for Kent, Leicestershire and Essex. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Leicestershire cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Chatham, Kent
